    "How many end devices would lose internet access if each routing device were to fail. Add a second router nearby to eliminate single points of failure." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the failure impact analysis.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
