    "This information helps you understand whether a device will work with other ecosystems if you switch platforms." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Denna information hjälper dig förstå om en enhet fungerar med andra ekosystem om du byter plattform."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This is distinct from the offline alert — it monitors the overall grade, not individual devices. Pair both for comprehensive coverage." : {
      "comment" : "User Manual tip distinguishing the background health watchdog from the offline alert.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
