    "Thread uses 2.4 GHz channels 11–26. Channels 15, 20, and 25 have the lowest overlap with Wi-Fi 2.4 GHz. Channels 11–14, 17–19, and 22–24 overlap with Wi-Fi non-overlapping channels 1, 6, and 11." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the thread channel analysis.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Thread använder 2,4 GHz-kanalerna 11–26. Kanalerna 15, 20 och 25 har lägst överlappning med Wi-Fi 2,4 GHz. Kanalerna 11–14, 17–19 och 22–24 överlappar Wi-Fis icke-överlappande kanaler 1, 6 och 11."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper" : {
      "comment" : "The name of the app.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "ThreadMapper adds a \"Thread Network\" button to Control Center (iOS 18+). Tapping it opens ThreadMapper directly. Add it via Settings → Control Center → Thread Network." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper lägger till en \"Thread-nätverk\"-knapp i Kontrollcenter (iOS 18+). Att trycka på den öppnar ThreadMapper direkt. Lägg till den via Inställningar → Kontrollcenter → Thread-nätverk."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper also provides a Lock Screen (accessory inline) widget that shows your current health grade letter and score in a compact single-line format. Add it via Customise Lock Screen." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper tillhandahåller också en Låsskärm (tillbehör inline) widget som visar ditt nuvarande hälsobetygsboktav och poäng i ett kompakt enradigt format. Lägg till den via Anpassa låsskärm."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper can send several categories of push notification:" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper kan skicka flera kategorier av push-aviseringar:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper continuously records mesh snapshots in the background (up to 720 frames, one per 50-minute interval). Open Mesh → Tools → Topology Time-Lapse to scrub through the history with a timeline slider or use the play/pause button to animate the changes." : {
      "comment" : "User Manual paragraph describing the topology time-lapse feature.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper spelar kontinuerligt in mesh-ögonblicksbilder i bakgrunden (upp till 720 bildrutor, en per 50-minutersintervall). Öppna Mesh → Verktyg → Topologi Timelapse för att bläddra igenom historiken med ett tidslinjereglag eller använd uppspelnings-/pausknappen för att animera ändringarna."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper Diagnostic Report" : {
      "comment" : "The title of a share sheet that allows the user to share a diagnostic report.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "ThreadMapper hasn't scanned yet. Open the app to check your devices." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper har inte skannat ännu. Öppna appen för att kontrollera dina enheter."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper hasn't scanned yet. Open the app to see your Thread network health." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper har inte skannat ännu. Öppna appen för att se din Thread-nätverkshälsa."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper includes built-in tips for popular Thread device brands. When you open a device detail for a recognised manufacturer, a Vendor Notes card appears with model-specific guidance." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper inkluderar inbyggda tips för populära Thread-enhetsmärken. När du öppnar enhetsdetaljer för en erkänd tillverkare visas ett Leverantörsanteckningar-kort med modellspecifik vägledning."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper logs every time you open the diagnostics sheet with the top-level result (Healthy / Issues Found / Critical). Tap \"Run History\" to see a timeline of past runs and spot when a problem first appeared or was resolved." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ThreadMapper loggar varje gång du öppnar diagnostikbladet med toppresultatet (Friskt / Problem hittade / Kritiskt). Tryck på \"Körningshistorik\" för att se en tidslinje över tidigare körningar och se när ett problem först dök upp eller löstes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ThreadMapper needs notification permission to alert you about device and network events." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the notification permissions required for the app.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
