      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tidsintervall"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Time-Lapse is most useful after a network incident — scrub back to the moment devices went offline to see what the topology looked like." : {
      "comment" : "User Manual tip for the topology time-lapse feature.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Timelapse är mest användbart efter en nätverksincident — spola tillbaka till det ögonblick enheterna gick offline för att se hur topologin såg ut."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To reduce hop count, place a Thread router roughly halfway between the deep device and its current parent." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "För att minska hoppantalet, placera en Thread-router ungefär halvvägs mellan den djupa enheten och dess nuvarande förälder."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To start fresh: clear all three stores in Settings → Data, then delete and reinstall the app. Your HomeKit home, devices, and Apple ID subscription are unaffected." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "För att börja om: rensa alla tre lager i Inställningar → Data, ta sedan bort och installera om appen. Ditt HomeKit-hem, enheter och Apple-ID-prenumeration är opåverkade."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Today" : {
      "comment" : "A label for the current day.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
