    },
    "You have %lld border routers. Create a Siri Shortcut that opens ThreadMapper when you notice smart home latency — this gives you an instant mesh health snapshot without manual diagnosis." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du har %lld gränssnittsroutrar. Skapa en Siri-genväg som öppnar ThreadMapper när du märker latens i smarthemmet – detta ger dig en omedelbar nätverkshälsöversikt utan manuell diagnos."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You have only one border router (%@). If it goes offline, your entire Thread mesh loses internet access. A second HomePod mini or Apple TV in a different room provides failover." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du har bara en gränssnittsrouter (%@). Om den går offline förlorar hela ditt Thread-nätverk internetåtkomsten. En andra HomePod mini eller Apple TV i ett annat rum ger redundans."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You'll also see the raw offline event count and the online streak — consecutive days since the last offline event." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du ser också det råa antalet offline-händelser och online-streaken — konsekutiva dagar sedan den senaste offline-händelsen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You're on a %lld-day Grade A streak — excellent!" : {
