    },
    "Your mesh has %lld devices but no dedicated Thread routers — all traffic routes directly to border routers. A mains-powered Thread device (Eve Energy, Nanoleaf panel, IKEA plug) placed centrally acts as a relay and dramatically improves mesh resilience." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ditt nätverk har %lld enheter men inga dedikerade Thread-routrar – all trafik går direkt till gränssnittsroutrarna. En elnätsansluten Thread-enhet (Eve Energy, Nanoleaf-panel, IKEA-plugg) placerad centralt fungerar som relä och förbättrar nätverkets motståndskraft avsevärt."
          }
        }
      }
    },
